  "body": "With the unknown nature of ASIC risk looming I'm wondering if there is a way to add telemetry to mining rewards so that secondary research of the collected telemetry could quantify specific ASIC behavior. I.e. nothing that directly combats ASIC, but something that can detect and locate ASIC farms and particulars of ASIC behavior. If this were possible, then a future targeted fork could directly combat ASIC behavior.",
